instr_1:
This is Section 2.

In this section, your task will be the same as before - that is, to type the word you see on the screen AFTER the typing prompt. However, rather than just seeing the word before typing, you will also see a video of someone typing different words to what you will need to type at different speeds. 

Press 'enter/return' to go to the next page.
instr_2:
This is Section 4. 

In this section, your task will be the same as before - that is, to type the word you see on the screen after the typing prompt. You will see a video again, like in Section 2, only this time, the video will show someone the same word that you must type at different speeds. 

Press 'enter/return' to go to the next page.
